<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="dist/img/favicon-32x32.png">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Big+Shoulders+Display:wght@700&family=Lexend+Deca&family=Press+Start+2P&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="dist/css/main.min.css">
    <title>Frontend Mentor | 3-column preview card component</title>

</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1 class="primary-heading">Welcome to my project with 3 js excercisess</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div class="main__wrapper">
            <div class="even-boxes__container">
                <section class="bg-primary--300">
                    <div class="even-boxes " data-includes="sedan-bg">
                        <h2 class="secondary-heading">SEDANS</h2>
                        <div class="even-boxes__description-container">
                            <p class="paragraph">Section called sedans reprsent a simple game "Guess number". The game
                                is
                                based on random number which the player must guess. Good luck!</p>
                            <a class="btn txt-primary--300" href="guess-number.html">Learn More</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <section class="bg-primary--400">
                    <div class="even-boxes" data-includes="suv-bg">
                        <h2 class="secondary-heading">SUVS</h2>
                        <div class="even-boxes__description-container">
                            <p class="paragraph">Modal window mini project - after clicking on one of three buttons you
                                can
                                open the modal window. Leeeeet's explore! </p>
                            <a class="btn txt-primary--400" href="modal-windows.html">Learn More</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <section class="bg-primary--900">
                    <div class="even-boxes" data-includes="luxury-bg">
                        <h2 class="secondary-heading">LUXURY</h2>
                        <div class="even-boxes__description-container">
                            <p class="paragraph">
                                Pig-game. 1 dot dice reset the
                                current score and switch to 2nd player. Hold button let you keep the current score. The
                                winner must collect 100 points.
                            </p>
                            <a class="btn txt-primary--900" href="pig-game.html">Learn More</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="attribution class=" paragraph"">
        Challenge by <a href="https://www.frontendmentor.io?ref=challenge" target="_blank">Frontend Mentor</a>.
        Coded by <a href="#">Joanna</a>. Games were made with Jonas Schmedtmann Complete Javascript Course.
    </footer>
    <script src="dist/js/main.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>